data.description:
In honor of tonight's presidential debate:
"Let me tell you something about towers. We have the best towers in the world. People love our towers. When people send their kids to Stanford, they're not sending their best. They're sending their losers. They're sending their worst people. And some, I assume, are good people. I will build a great wall around Stanford and I will make Stanford pay for that wall. Mark my words. And let me tell you about Dirks. I know where he put the public funds. Right next to Hillary Clinton's emails. Well, Dirks, I've got something to tell you. You're Fired(tm). I have a great relationship with the bears. The bears love me. I've said if Oski wasn't our mascot, perhaps I'd be dating him. If I become chancellor, I will stop all clown immigration into Berkeley until we can implement extreme vetting. If I was president I would bomb the shit out of those killer clowns. We are going to Make Cal Great Again."
-Trumpinile
